name: generic
purpose: visual style contract for PPT generation
palette: neutral background, restrained accent, high contrast body text
typography: title 28-36pt, body 14-18pt, metric 44-72pt
layout_rules:
  - one core message per slide
  - prefer metric, comparison, timeline, framework, and action-plan layouts
  - split slides when bullets exceed six
content_rules:
  - style file is not content evidence
  - never use template sample text as final slide content
